CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 24, 1956, pg. A26 reads: "Teen Queen Contest Going Great - With the 1956 Hill Top Teen Queen contest getting into its stride..."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Janice Prentice wearing light colored v-neck sweater and hoop earrings, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Marlene Hopkins wearing a light colored blouse with plaid collar, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest
